grep -r "CEST\|CET" lib/ scripts/ test/
```

**🚨 IMMEDIATE ACTION REQUIRED:**
1. Update all existing scripts to use local time
2. Create LocalTime module for consistent usage
3. Audit all timestamp generation code
4. Update git commit messages to use local time
5. Ensure all new code follows local time rule

