## 🚀 **PCIS: Phoenix Container Integration System**
**Architecture**: Local-first development with comprehensive testing via Claude AI agents and TPS methodology
**Components**: `lib/pcis/local_first/` (rules, session_state, database, volumes), validation/monitoring systems, hybrid Ubuntu+NixOS architecture
**Rules**: Relative data paths, no external mounts, local DB directories, project-only storage, zero tolerance enforcement
