**VALIDATION SUCCESS REQUIRES:**
1. ✅ All 5 methods executed
2. ✅ 100% consensus achieved
3. ✅ Audit trail created
4. ✅ STAMP constraints satisfied
5. ✅ No drift detected
6. ✅ Report generated

**ANY FAILURE = IMMEDIATE HALT**

