Based on comprehensive 5-level analysis (documented in `docs/journal/20250910-1351-comprehensive-nixos-container-setup-5level-analysis.md`), the Intelitor project has achieved enterprise-grade container infrastructure with complete validation and testing frameworks.

### **🛡️ Core Container Infrastructure (MANDATORY USAGE)**

**✅ VERIFIED CONTAINER SETUP:**
- **Production Script**: `scripts/containers/verified_nixos_setup.exs` - Complete 6-phase setup process
- **SSL Certificate Strategy**: Multi-path certificate symlink resolution for Erlang/OTP compatibility
- **Container Registry Enforcement**: Localhost-only registry with zero tolerance for external pulls
- **PHICS Integration**: Hot-reloading container system with bidirectional file sync
- **Health Monitoring**: Real-time container health validation with automatic recovery

**✅ COMPREHENSIVE TESTING FRAMEWORK:**
- **STAMP Safety Tests**: `test/stamp/container_safety_constraints_test.exs` - 5 critical safety constraints
- **TDG Container Tests**: `test/tdg/container_creation_test.exs` - Test-driven generation methodology
- **Property-Based Tests**: `test/property/container_properties_test.exs` - Dual PropCheck/ExUnitProperties validation

